{"tid":1118964,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"老貓唔肯食乾糧 體重下降","createTime":"2019-04-21T15:51:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-23T11:37:50.000Z","uid":136537,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6581c3bd45748f407bca8d2ec9e51c59ea954202","tid":1118964,"uid":136537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T15:51:04.000Z","msg":"13歲 18年8月驗過血 有第一期腎病<br />\n之後都多左餵濕糧<br />\n<br />\n但到呢幾日 突然唔肯食乾糧<br />\n晚晚去到12點就係咁叫我地餵濕糧<br />\n(之前無試過咁)<br />\n體重岩岩一磅 由3.5kg -&gt;2.8kg<br />\n水keep住平時份量咁飲<br />\n小便正常 但明顯見到大便好乾 <br />\n份量亦比平時少(便秘?)<br />\n好擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽日會打電話book睇醫生<br />\n<br />\n有無人貓貓試過咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fi08PMy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffi08PMy.png&h=760cdc11&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"865af7b57f85192439807d1b18363a461941d9df","tid":1118964,"uid":136537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T16:22:07.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"9f05d67c7b9a5f244e06d62ece231369908fe8ba","tid":1118964,"uid":89868,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T16:26:03.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我屋企隻貓都老了"},{"pid":"6380a172b49834b83c759bf1b7d1958e4c9d9a5b","tid":1118964,"uid":136537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f05d67c7b9a5f244e06d62ece231369908fe8ba","tid":1118964,"uid":89868,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T16:26:03.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我屋企隻貓都老了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T16:33:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d1bd4f6e3932ffb63c5f7540fdcb84ef72ebb2f","tid":1118964,"uid":21757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T18:39:17.000Z","msg":"腎病要低蛋白，唔應該食濕糧<br />\n忍心餓佢，肚餓自然食<br />\n問下獸醫議見"},{"pid":"7766a2759aa73fa101e2ddfecb87e7aa53ee29de","tid":1118964,"uid":38033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T11:49:37.000Z","msg":"腎貓會有好多併發病，貧血胰臟炎結石之類，會唔會係痛所以唔食野呀"},{"pid":"c187319e62ffeeb1b47a000fa2eaa647ebd74295","tid":1118964,"uid":38033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d1bd4f6e3932ffb63c5f7540fdcb84ef72ebb2f","tid":1118964,"uid":21757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T18:39:17.000Z","msg":"腎病要低蛋白，唔應該食濕糧<br />\n忍心餓佢，肚餓自然食<br />\n問下獸醫議見"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T11:50:29.000Z","msg":"腎病先要餵濕糧啦，唔打皮下水邊度黎水俾佢排毒"},{"pid":"2a28e0f9b017e38250dcd869e6172feb231c8b13","tid":1118964,"uid":16567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T11:57:34.000Z","msg":"會唔會牙齒問題？"},{"pid":"afa7723969d245dfe7e779181b689202eb24ae98","tid":1118964,"uid":98320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T11:58:53.000Z","msg":"想問下貓味年輕個陣食邊一隻糧？<br />\n想參考下"},{"pid":"b78d0fa67eea222447a27bc2370603d11ba37754","tid":1118964,"uid":21757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c187319e62ffeeb1b47a000fa2eaa647ebd74295","tid":1118964,"uid":38033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d1bd4f6e3932ffb63c5f7540fdcb84ef72ebb2f","tid":1118964,"uid":21757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T18:39:17.000Z","msg":"腎病要低蛋白，唔應該食濕糧<br />\n忍心餓佢，肚餓自然食<br />\n問下獸醫議見"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T11:50:29.000Z","msg":"腎病先要餵濕糧啦，唔打皮下水邊度黎水俾佢排毒"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T17:58:42.000Z","msg":"如果食濕糧要食獸醫配方或低蛋白質<br />\n如果隻貓唔飲水濕糧水份唔夠，可以問獸醫 貓每天要多少水 加水落啲濕糧度，唔好餵一次 每天最少三餐 會平均啲"},{"pid":"4ef96b6c80aa9ee6434eedfabaf77ea7d6712aff","tid":1118964,"uid":116807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T18:08:08.000Z","msg":"腎貓都有處方濕糧架<br />\n本來餵嘅乾糧要停啦<br />\n同埋食降磷藥會好易便秘 <br />\n要睇住佢飲唔飲得夠水"},{"pid":"d5b75b8c34cffa132f4551f319b4a8db614bed65","tid":1118964,"uid":191988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5d1bd4f6e3932ffb63c5f7540fdcb84ef72ebb2f","tid":1118964,"uid":21757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T18:39:17.000Z","msg":"腎病要低蛋白，唔應該食濕糧<br />\n忍心餓佢，肚餓自然食<br />\n問下獸醫議見"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T18:18:12.000Z","msg":"不是低蛋白，因為低蛋白會令到老貓冇肌肉<br />\n咁佢哋就會好易攰<br />\n正確啲來講係要食優質蛋白<br />\n有很多人喂生肉糧腎指數會變靚仔左<br />\n因為生肉含優質蛋白同埋大量水份<br />\n比較關鍵既係低磷<br />\n因為有腎病嘅腎代謝唔到高磷<br />\n所以會大大增加腎嘅負擔<br />\n樓主不防上fb哩個group睇睇<br />\n有好大量嘅有用資訊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0tDiBmG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0tDiBmG.png&h=f57fb0c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n基本上低磷飲食，小食多餐，同埋水份就係最需要嘅嘢。任何老貓都應該停止食用乾糧。乾糧無水份=餅乾，重要有多重程序去製造。當中既營養已經流失好多，更加唔係優質蛋白。"},{"pid":"d2b22df31fc8fad6dba1ed627d5ada266826707c","tid":1118964,"uid":191988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T18:22:27.000Z","msg":"From fb group 貓豬藍藍慢性腎衰竭的生活札記<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CetB7u7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCetB7u7.png&h=105c58bb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2n5ADBO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2n5ADBO.png&h=9a4a3110&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ee6b37099c63e68ae89ea1702e6e1fdea726e69e","tid":1118964,"uid":191988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b78d0fa67eea222447a27bc2370603d11ba37754","tid":1118964,"uid":21757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c187319e62ffeeb1b47a000fa2eaa647ebd74295","tid":1118964,"uid":38033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d1bd4f6e3932ffb63c5f7540fdcb84ef72ebb2f","tid":1118964,"uid":21757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T18:39:17.000Z","msg":"腎病要低蛋白，唔應該食濕糧<br />\n忍心餓佢，肚餓自然食<br />\n問下獸醫議見"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T11:50:29.000Z","msg":"腎病先要餵濕糧啦，唔打皮下水邊度黎水俾佢排毒"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T17:58:42.000Z","msg":"如果食濕糧要食獸醫配方或低蛋白質<br />\n如果隻貓唔飲水濕糧水份唔夠，可以問獸醫 貓每天要多少水 加水落啲濕糧度，唔好餵一次 每天最少三餐 會平均啲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T18:26:52.000Z","msg":"普遍獸醫配方嗰種濕糧成份差到喊<br />\n低蛋白會令到貓隻消瘦肌肉不足<br />\n蛋白質方面只要正常及是優質蛋白就可以了<br />\n反而低磷係重點"},{"pid":"240685dc4afb8b8cb3b52fc07c07d9259834b0d2","tid":1118964,"uid":21757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee6b37099c63e68ae89ea1702e6e1fdea726e69e","tid":1118964,"uid":191988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b78d0fa67eea222447a27bc2370603d11ba37754","tid":1118964,"uid":21757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c187319e62ffeeb1b47a000fa2eaa647ebd74295","tid":1118964,"uid":38033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T11:50:29.000Z","msg":"腎病先要餵濕糧啦，唔打皮下水邊度黎水俾佢排毒"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T17:58:42.000Z","msg":"如果食濕糧要食獸醫配方或低蛋白質<br />\n如果隻貓唔飲水濕糧水份唔夠，可以問獸醫 貓每天要多少水 加水落啲濕糧度，唔好餵一次 每天最少三餐 會平均啲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T18:26:52.000Z","msg":"普遍獸醫配方嗰種濕糧成份差到喊<br />\n低蛋白會令到貓隻消瘦肌肉不足<br />\n蛋白質方面只要正常及是優質蛋白就可以了<br />\n反而低磷係重點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T18:31:34.000Z","msg":"明白"},{"pid":"3d0cbd25d13261d8ef41df191c8e387d74be8f8e","tid":1118964,"uid":60785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T18:44:30.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"d0c524d04ae984173dd34b20c8251ce509403130","tid":1118964,"uid":168217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T19:22:09.000Z","msg":"Google 貓鮮食磚<br />\n希望幫到佢"},{"pid":"381b4dd21574a658b8ec181008a2126522922dff","tid":1118964,"uid":86442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T11:37:50.000Z","msg":"唔好下下食處方糧.....生肉會係比較好既選擇"}]}